summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of Lot 10, Block 2, Burke's 2nd Addition; Lots 5 and 6, Block 1, Replat of Oneida Gardens Addition; Lot 3, Block 2, Denny and Hoyt's Addition; portion of the south 310 feet of the northwest quarter of northeast quarter of Section 3, Township 23 North, Range 4 East, W. M., and Lots 6 to 10 inclusive, Block 14, Woodlawn Addition to Green Lake; with respect to Use, Height and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto three new section numbered 2-190, 10-9 and 17-139, respectively.
